fr.cines.eudat.repopack.rp_core

Class DataObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.cines.eudat.repopack.rp_core.DataObject

  • public class DataObject
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a data object from the repository. Even if the data object is replicated as a file, additional information (some metadata) describes the object and its replication. Getter and setter methods are available to handle the different properties NOTE : This class has the potential to be extended with additional metadata
    Author:
    "S. Coutin (CINES)"
